org.apache.drill.exec.store.easy.json.parser

Class RootParser.EmbeddedObjectParser

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.drill.exec.store.easy.json.parser.RootParser
      • org.apache.drill.exec.store.easy.json.parser.RootParser.EmbeddedObjectParser
  • Enclosing class:
    RootParser

    public static class RootParser.EmbeddedObjectParser
extends RootParser
    Parser for data embedded within a message structure which is encoded as a single JSON object. Example: 
    
 { status: "ok", results: { ... } }

    The parser counts over the single object. The message parser will parse any content after the closing bracket.
